#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.24:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.24:0.2"
msgid "3. Puggalavagga"
msgstr "3. Persons"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Bahukārasutta"
msgstr "24. Very Helpful"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.24:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, puggalā puggalassa bahukārā."
msgstr "Mendicants, these three people are very helpful to another."

msgctxt "an3.24:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.24:1.3"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, bhikkhave, puggalaṃ āgamma puggalo buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti, dhammaṃ "
"saraṇaṃ gato hoti, saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti;"
msgstr ""
"The person who has enabled you to go for refuge to the Buddha, the teaching, "
"and the Saṅgha."

msgctxt "an3.24:1.4"
msgid "ayaṃ, bhikkhave, puggalo imassa puggalassa bahukāro."
msgstr "This person is very helpful to another."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.24:2.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, yaṃ puggalaṃ āgamma puggalo ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti "
"yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodho’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti "
"yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti;"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the person who has enabled you to truly understand: ‘This is "
"suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of "
"suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "an3.24:2.2"
msgid "ayaṃ, bhikkhave, puggalo imassa puggalassa bahukāro."
msgstr "This person is very helpful to another."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.24:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, yaṃ puggalaṃ āgamma puggalo āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ "
"cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharati;"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the person who has enabled you to realize the undefiled freedom "
"of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life, and live having realized "
"it with your own insight due to the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "an3.24:3.2"
msgid "ayaṃ, bhikkhave, puggalo imassa puggalassa bahukāro."
msgstr "This person is very helpful to another."

msgctxt "an3.24:3.3"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo puggalā puggalassa bahukārā."
msgstr "These are the three people who are very helpful to another person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.24:4.1"
msgid ""
"Imehi ca pana, bhikkhave, tīhi puggalehi imassa puggalassa natthañño puggalo "
"bahukāroti vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"And I say that there is no-one more helpful to another than these three "
"people."

msgctxt "an3.24:4.2"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ pana, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ puggalānaṃ iminā puggalena na suppatikāraṃ "
"vadāmi, yadidaṃ abhivādanapaccuṭṭhānaañjalikammasāmīcikammacīvarapiṇḍapātasen"
"āsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānuppadānenā”ti."
msgstr ""
"And I also say that it’s not easy to repay these three people by bowing down "
"to them, rising up for them, greeting them with joined palms, and observing "
"proper etiquette for them; or by providing them with robes, alms-food, "
"lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.24:4.3"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
